name: PREGNANT BITCH
description: P.B is an art of a teenage girl.After becoming pregnant,she began to swallow emergency contraceptives but it didn’t help.Having an abortion isn’t an option.Now she is a conveyor of swallowing pills.She is dreaming to get rid of the child.The shape of her skull is similar as that of an embryo.She is emaciated from stress but have a huge belly.The puppet in the hand is the image of the past,which is becoming less and even has already jumped out of the body,remaining on the thin strings of memory
